0.1.name: wordpress/itunes-lookup-widget
0.1.description: Embeds an interactive iTunes display as a sidebar widget with optional use of affiliate links. Multilingual Frontend (just update labels in admin settings page and/or widget as required) Shortcode enabled. (use link within widget in widget admin to get the shortcode for the settings selected)
